    • Method Detail

      • init

        protected void init()
        The structure of the configuration file (for backwards compatibility) is 
             {"config":[comments],
       "qdl" : {"scripts" : [{"script":{...}}, {"script":{...}},...]}
      }
        The assumption is that this is handed the qdl config object and can start pulling it apart at that level.
